Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a cool place or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're special, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ugly dogs in my fan\Nclub don't know about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disgusting, you vulgar,\Narrogant, retarded celebrity punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you have some TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like being kicked\Nby a retarded celebrity punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You old bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stinking perfume makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the disgusting one, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sue you for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My son is an excellent lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A punk like you will\Nbe squashed like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We found traces of two bullets...\Nin the chest and in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see signs of blood under the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been a very special gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets exploded inside his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Better check those bullet fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the medical team here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all in the hospital\Nbecause of food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of our tax money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably shocked to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an autopsy just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this guy's a celebrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He has seven TV shows a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a popular comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,His usual material is about corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna laugh at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tearjerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He was such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why would anyone kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the nicest guy I ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand breaking\Nup our team like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata at the studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His outraged fans are\Nrushing to the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see how popular he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, according to our sources,\Nthis case may involve organized crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for that old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People die everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have enough problems already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more punctual, Oburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've called someone else in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the one in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one will take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them are child molesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to pay for what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one besides me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this weekend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me when you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know our usual activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife just isn't\Ngood enough, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The reward for each\Nadult is the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it from Kanie later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You stink, Mr. Akai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oburi, I don't have\Nan easy job, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The stink from the corpses\Nmakes my eyes water all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And that rotten smell is so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder I always stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think about what I asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hold you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your generosity makes me feel weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have to take\Ncare of three more jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between you and me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to be fair to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanie, I'll do my best to be on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, give us the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got my jacket dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that nice, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and wash it yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,1 05 yen is your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You look good in that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a new flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked Kanie\Nwhere I worked part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As in ''the sand you can't hold''\Nand ''the feather blown by the wind.''
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Oburi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanie told me your name, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Oburi your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very unusual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alike, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Akai to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...my guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those earrings\Nmust be very special to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wearing\Nthem the last time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They look weird, yet really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...made from the\Nblood of my papa and mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of my lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Hollywood movie star, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of my classmates are fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know that\Nhe had a twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be here in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the third celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get the wrong one, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He has three bodyguards, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I get him?
